= News (Detail)
== News page is now available on Hiki
((*Posted by Masao on 2003-10-22 (Wed) 17:55:02*))

I added a new feature to this site(English site only).
It can create news pages easily(This is a feature for Writer on this Hiki).

News pages are added from ((<create_news>)) page.
You can write news with RD+ style.

Recent news is shown in ((<FrontPage>)).
Other news are shown in ((<News>)) page.
((<News>)) page shows each News headlines.
If you want to read more, click "Read more".
You can also access each news as a page.
